{"tid":1181021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[回帶] 支那客人問我，今年怎麼不再叫毋忘六四","createTime":"2019-06-01T09:31:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T09:38:03.000Z","uid":7555,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6a63431c8690dd8a5ff171d41432107364e05f43","tid":1181021,"uid":7555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T09:31:16.000Z","msg":"支那的客人問我，今年怎麼不再叫「毋忘六四」，我回答：「那是支那的事，你們自己去爭取好了，我會旁觀支持你們，但不再干我的事了」<br />\r\n一直堅持那是美國佬陰謀的他竟慌了：「怎麼不干你的事，你是支那人呀！」"},{"pid":"4d1cb9106e94600ce93f2a52d8229c6298a4aef9","tid":1181021,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T09:38:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/20/191007_7354238acb51a149c52f6bfe97c51bdc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F20%2F191007_7354238acb51a149c52f6bfe97c51bdc.jpg&h=bc74cc9b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}